Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 繪瑠是這麼報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過去跟他說說話會不會好點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得先放他一段時間比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來受傷很重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是想要讓司打起精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你真的向艾拉告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然把你叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你… 那個… 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司真的向你告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我聽說你拒絕他了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被告 告 告白了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你完全看起來不像沒事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腦子裡跳出了許多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順勢就告訴他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之後司就一直那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我向他搭話似乎也聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他那樣子不管誰去搭話都一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是艾拉需要在意的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該說司最近有些得意忘形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會變成這樣肯定大概就是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是不會看氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然就跑出來告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和司在嘉年華會場上走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看吧果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連好好保護女生都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點用都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他非常拚命地找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 這是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之後就開始放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們一起牽著手看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那時候牽手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還不錯…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後順著話題就被抱住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:05:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是激情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這一點都不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定要拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我傷害了司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉想怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是滿會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得就算你問她也沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿又沒有被人告白過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夠了 別在那多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在司面前你還能像以前一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想兩個人都應該先冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要試試跟司分開過幾天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話你也可以好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對他到底是怎樣的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具體怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…現在正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來你沒有計劃啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的目標需要小心一點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者引起過暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有前科的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說…你知道司向艾拉告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼！ 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司求婚時說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是求婚 是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個傢伙 進展到什麼程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說進展…是指的什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概…知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉似乎拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的表情很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}閉嘴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是擅自動房間的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不會輕易饒過你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是司做了任何一點可疑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把他趕出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿的內衣放在這邊的抽屜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那邊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告訴他幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 為什麼我和司住一間房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的司氣氛那麼沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暫且忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男生和女生換一下房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要和繪瑠一起照顧艾拉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安慰司就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用做到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算消沉到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我爽快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被甩掉而已有什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正不理你 你也只會坐在那裡什麼都不吃發呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我的房間餓死了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎麼覺得一晚上不吃不喝也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃吧 趁著還沒有涼快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁著還沒有涼趕快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比…比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你給我穿這件衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉竟然會來我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夢想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全冷靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克 太不像話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不認真工作卻一心搞職場戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}區區一個新人太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是現在還把自己當學生的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我無話可說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你很受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要把工作和私生活分開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在像你這樣的廢柴 去回收和家人一樣的吉芙提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別人會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你說過我爸爸變成遊蕩者的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我眼睜睜的失去父親 變成孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然香月姐來看過我很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就對她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「你不用再來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為吉芙提爾和持有者提供心靈依靠是終端服務的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我雖然不能代替你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是至少能陪你說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你振作起來之前希望你讓我這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然我沒辦法面對你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到那樣的香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才想加入終端服務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我為自己在這裡工作感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以如果你在這裡混日子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我饒不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我只是作為一個前輩指導你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告白之後後悔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然被拒絕了 但是對艾拉的感情不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還挺執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得你這點很帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為…為什麼我剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說你真的懂我在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂的話就別在那裡發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好想想今後怎麼和艾拉接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}真的是愛管閒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什麼了說出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會聽著的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 今晚不會讓你睡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來開睡衣派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…滿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下就會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了艾拉拉我準備了這麼多的睡衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從哪個開始穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 從哪個開始？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被看見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 沒想到竟然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不快點準備的話要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼不早點叫我起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總覺得…有點怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是我該在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對 我們並沒有做什麼下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 司和滿很般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 要趕快追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解開了誤會真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我太衝動弄錯了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 要怪也怪我沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別不說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易有這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好聊一下怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我那時候拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再給我一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是無論艾拉作何決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請至少讓我繼續做你的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什麼在意的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你覺得戀愛是不是氣勢也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是指艾拉的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我讓那孩子好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種事花費太多時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會向著壞的方向考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…究竟怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是什麼茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你實際上是怎麼看待司的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼司總是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一開始讓我在意的是這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前滿不是也說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司可能是因為悲傷而笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想讓他有那樣的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總想著要幫他些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是去遊樂園的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從中途心就怦怦地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一想到司的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心裡就充滿緊張和悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒辦法用語言來形容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎是嗎 果然是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經得到答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自己也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 答案早已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然 那就趕快去和司說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}我要離開司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得這樣做對彼此都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話我就跟你明說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你感覺到的這種悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是戀愛 是戀愛的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以根本不需要離開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更要遠離司了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不懂 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告訴我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣才能得出這樣的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為…一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我只剩下大概一個月的壽命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喲 你居然沒喝醉真是罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別那麼瞪著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是嫌我礙事的話 我會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是不是煽動司了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煽動什麼的 太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只是自己想清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像個男人一樣表達出自己的心意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果就是那個德行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們倆好不容易才合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼你是打算干涉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然至今一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有這種時候才會裝得像個前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這人對於可愛的後輩的事情可是一清二楚的喲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在這種地方幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉壽命的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你什麼時候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明明什麼都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卻對你和艾拉儘說些自作聰明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明應該在工作上已經適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說是最近才知道壽命的事的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在告白之前 還是之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你是明明知道還去告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做了這個工作以後 到底都看到了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分手是注定的 而你為什麼還要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想創造和艾拉在一起的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想為艾拉創造回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 我也想為她做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要做的是非常痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能會有什麼好結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 你也能毫不退縮地面對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我在爸爸的那時候逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒能面對他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此傷害了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能夠負責到底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經決定 要一直做艾拉的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直到最後的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}責任的意義 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和那時的我完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是這樣我才說外行完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在說你是個無藥可救的戀愛新手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我就稍微支持一下你們的戀愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好謝謝我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我被香月叫了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從今天起 你們兩個解除搭檔關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒聽清楚嗎 解除搭檔關係
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
